headline: 2 Dividend Kings to Buy for a Lifetime of Passive Income
summary: Dividend Kings are among the best income stocks on the market.  Let's consider two companies in this elite group with the exact qualities long-term income investors want: Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO) and Abbott Laboratories (NYSE: ABT).  Few businesses are better known worldwide than Coca-Cola.
